playstore_details.title: Pinkfong Singing Phone
playstore_details.description:
Ring, ring, Pinkfong's calling you! 

Teach your kids how to use a smartphone!

[Pinkfong Singing Phone] is an interactive phone app where kids can pick up & answer calls from Pinkfong.
Listen to exciting songs and use cute emojis to chat with Pinkfong! Use colorful frames to take selfies too. 
All of these are offered for FREE.

🔸Features🔸

1. Pick up the phone!
- Learn how to pick up the phone to chat with Pinkfong
- Sing along to popular Pinkfong songs, including Baby Shark!
- Receive random surprise calls.

2. Send funny messages!
- Use variety of emojis, including animals, food and hearts to text Pinkfong.
- Receive back texts from Pinkfong.

3. Learn how to dial numbers!
- Learn how to dial safely.
- Learn numbers from 0 to 9 in various tones.
- Choose among various instrument versions -- piano, violin, flute, and more!

4. Take selfies!
- Use colorful frames and backgrounds to take photos with Pinkfong.
- Easy to save and share pictures.

Have FUN!!!
playstore_details.summary: Call PINKFONG and talk, sing, take pictures together!
